                     <interp inst="t17720429-18-off97" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17720429-18-off97" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a japanned tea-tray, value 16 s. three India window-blinds, value 31 s. five glass cruets and three silver caps, value 18 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17720429-18-victim217" type="victimName">
                           Francis
                            Bradley
